Package: lmPrettyPlots
Type: Package
Title: Makes Pretty Versions of lm Regression Diagnostic Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Helen", "Greatrex",
      email = "hgreatrex@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides visually appealing residual diagnostic plots for linear models.
    The primary function generates studentized residual plots to assess model assumptions, 
    detect outliers, and evaluate linearity. 
